---
import DashboardLayout from '../layouts/DashboardLayout.astro';
import AgentStats from '../components/AgentStats';
---
<DashboardLayout title="Essaim d'Agents" currentPath="/swarm">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto space-y-8">
    <div class="flex justify-between items-end">
      <div>
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-2 tracking-tight">État de l'Essaim</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-400">Supervision en temps réel des 14 agents spécialisés de la Forge.</p>
      </div>
      <button class="btn btn-primary shadow-lg shadow-blue-500/20 flex items-center gap-2">
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 4v5h.582m15.356 2A8.001 8.001 0 004.582 9m0 0H9m11 11v-5h-.581m0 0a8.003 8.003 0 01-15.357-2m15.357 2H15"/></svg>
        Forcer un Audit Global
      </button>
    </div>
    
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 xl:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <div class="xl:col-span-1">
        <AgentStats client:load />
      </div>
      
      <div class="xl:col-span-2 space-y-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-900/50 border border-slate-800 rounded-xl p-6 backdrop-blur-sm">
          <h3 class="font-bold text-white mb-6 border-b border-slate-800 pb-3 uppercase tracking-widest text-xs text-slate-500">Activités Récentes des Agents</h3>
          <div class="space-y-6">
            <div class="flex gap-4 group">
              <div class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-blue-400 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(96,165,250,0.8)] shrink-0"></div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white group-hover:text-blue-400 transition">DEV_FRONTEND a modifié <span class="text-blue-400 font-mono text-xs bg-blue-500/10 px-1 rounded">index.astro</span></p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1 leading-relaxed">Correction de la responsivité du header et mise en place du système de drawer DaisyUI.</p>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-600 font-mono mt-2 block uppercase">Il y a 5 minutes</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex gap-4 group border-t border-slate-800/50 pt-6">
              <div class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-emerald-400 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(52,211,153,0.8)] shrink-0"></div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white group-hover:text-emerald-400 transition">CHEF_TECHNIQUE a activé <span class="text-emerald-400 font-mono text-xs bg-emerald-500/10 px-1 rounded">/api/settings.ts</span></p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1 leading-relaxed">Déploiement du nouveau pont de configuration pour la gestion des jetons Vercel et GitHub.</p>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-600 font-mono mt-2 block uppercase">Il y a 12 minutes</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="flex gap-4 group border-t border-slate-800/50 pt-6">
              <div class="mt-1.5 w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-amber-400 shadow-[0_0_8px_rgba(251,191,36,0.8)] shrink-0"></div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-sm font-medium text-white group-hover:text-amber-400 transition">INFRA_TECH vérifie <span class="text-amber-400 font-mono text-xs bg-amber-500/10 px-1 rounded">docker-compose.yml</span></p>
                <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 mt-1 leading-relaxed">Audit de conformité ZimaOS sur les volumes montés et les permissions socket.</p>
                <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-600 font-mono mt-2 block uppercase">Il y a 1 heure</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4">
           <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-widest">Tâches complétées</span>
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-1">124</div>
           </div>
           <div class="bg-slate-900 border border-slate-800 p-4 rounded-xl">
              <span class="text-[10px] text-slate-500 uppercase font-bold tracking-widest">Temps de calcul</span>
              <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mt-1">42h <span class="text-sm font-normal text-slate-500">ce mois</span></div>
           </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</DashboardLayout>
